Class OIndexTxAwareDictionary

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OIndex, OIndexInternal, Comparable<OIndex>

    public class OIndexTxAwareDictionary
extends OIndexTxAwareOneValue
    Transactional wrapper for dictionary index. Stores changes locally to the transaction until tx.commit(). All the other operations are delegated to the wrapped OIndex instance.
    Author:
    Luca Garulli (l.garulli--(at)--orientdb.com)
